org.zoolu.sip.dialog

Class DialogInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zoolu.sip.dialog.DialogInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Dialog

    public class DialogInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class DialogInfo maintains a complete information status of a generic SIP dialog. It has the following attributes:
    • sip-provider
    • call-id
    • local and remote URLs
    • local and remote contact URLs
    • local and remote cseqs
    • local and remote tags
    • dialog-id
    • route set
